OL,3,CStuart Broad sets sights on budding
OL,4,Cpub chain after retiring from cricket
OL,6,FBroad announced his retirement from
OL,7,Fcricket during the fifth and final
OL,8,FAshes Test against Australia last
OL,9,Fsummer.
OL,11,FStuart now co-owns two pubs ` the Tap
OL,12,F& Run in Nottinghamshire and The
OL,13,FGriffin Inn in Leicestershire ` with
OL,14,Ffellow former England cricketer Harry
OL,15,FGurney.
OL,17,FThe pair are targeting opening another
OL,18,Ffive pubs over the next five years,
OL,19,Fhaving gained investment from Lee
OL,20,FCash, the co-founder of Peach Pubs.
