OL,3,CStuart Broad sets sights on budding
OL,4,Cpub chain after retiring from cricket
OL,6,F"I realised you have to be open to the
OL,7,Ffact that it will hurt because your
OL,8,Fdream is over in a sense ... the thing
OL,9,Fyou've worked for since you're a kid
OL,10,Fis done, which is unusual, but that is
OL,11,Fsport.
OL,13,F"I think it's really important when
OL,14,Fyou're playing professional sport to
OL,15,Fhave half an eye on what's next,
OL,16,Fbecause if it comes with an injury or
OL,17,Fa loss of form, and you've not even
OL,18,Fthought about it once, then that's a
OL,19,Fhugely panicky situation to be in.
