OL,3,CStuart Broad sets sights on budding
OL,4,Cpub chain after retiring from cricket
OL,6,F"It would take me away from my family
OL,7,Fas much as being a player ... so that
OL,8,Fdoesn't quite fit for me right now,
OL,9,Fbut it might do in the future".
OL,11,FThe cricketer said it took several
OL,12,Fyears for the pair to find their feet
OL,13,Fas business owners and eventually
OL,14,Fdecided to focus on building a strong
OL,15,Fculture among staff in their pubs.
OL,17,F"The culture of the staff is number
OL,18,Fone, like it would be in a cricket
OL,19,Fchanging room," he said.
